Fix semconv schema URL conflict with otel SDK v1.43.0.

The otel SDK v1.43.0 aligns with semconv v1.40.0, but descheduler imports
semconv v1.39.0. When both are used in resource.New(), the conflicting
schema URLs cause resource detection to fail. Update the import to match
the SDK's semconv version.

diff --git a/pkg/tracing/tracing.go b/pkg/tracing/tracing.go
--- a/pkg/tracing/tracing.go
+++ b/pkg/tracing/tracing.go
@@ -28,7 +28,7 @@
 	"go.opentelemetry.io/otel/propagation"
 	sdkresource "go.opentelemetry.io/otel/sdk/resource"
 	sdktrace "go.opentelemetry.io/otel/sdk/trace"
-	semconv "go.opentelemetry.io/otel/semconv/v1.39.0"
+	semconv "go.opentelemetry.io/otel/semconv/v1.40.0"
 	"go.opentelemetry.io/otel/trace"
 	"go.opentelemetry.io/otel/trace/noop"
 	"google.golang.org/grpc/credentials"
